SAINTlogin,allows,users,to,log,in,to,a,website,or,to,a,private,network,by,dialing,a,number,on,their,cell,phones,rather,than,by,using,passwords,and,user,IDs,The,call,is,free,since,the,system,hangs,up,after,the,first,ring,If,the,caller,is,recognized,a,private,session,is,established,and,access,to,the,requested,pages,is,granted,The,SAINTlogin,API,enables,developers,to,integrate,SAINTlogin,with,their,websites,Doing,so,requires,the,use,of,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format